text: Gafurovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Gafurovsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 1,083 as of 2010. There are 25 streets. == Geography == It is located 10 km from Tuymazy, 11 km from Duslyk. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Gafurovo
